data.description: Beautiful home on a large corner lot located on a desirable court with your own swimming pool and spa, a perfect opportunity to live the good life, plus great for entertaining too with a large patio, gated pool and inside has a separate family room and additional living room for gatherings. Curb appeal is here with manicured landscaping and beautiful brick exterior on the front side. Enter the home to the living and 2nd dining room areas, featuring a gas fireplace. The large kitchen features custom pull-out drawers, plenty of cabinets, a large island with breakfast bar, the main eating area and plenty of natural light. The main suite has a separate shower and tub, recessed lighting and a walk-in closet. Plenty of storage throughout this home and the 3 car garage has cabinets on both sides. Enjoy gated community living in a wonderful location, also close to the west gate, shopping and more.
